<number id="3DE324FF4858FFA0FD52FCC4FD61FC8E" box="[644,708,858,884]" pageId="2" pageNumber="24" value="2006.0">2006</number>
</date>
(J. Layme leg.). Ecologically, the habitat corresponds to a former lower mountain forest (now reduced to a secondary forest due to farming). The 
