<emphasis id="B95FEACA4859FFA1FEF7F989FD96F9D4" box="[289,563,1559,1582]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="25">Chromatophotina awajun</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A26C57B14859FFA1FDECF988FDD2F9D4" box="[570,631,1558,1582]" pageId="3" pageNumber="25" rank="species">
<emphasis id="B95FEACA4859FFA1FDECF988FDD2F9D4" bold="true" box="[570,631,1558,1582]" pageId="3" pageNumber="25">n. sp.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
: A, male holotype (dorsal habitus); B, female paratype (dorsal habitus); C, female paratype, living specimen. 
<taxonomicName id="4C2B4D5B4859FFA1FDD0F9A9FCA1F9B4" box="[518,772,1591,1614]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Chromatophotina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="3" pageNumber="25" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cofan" status="n. sp.">
